Charles Stanley First-Half Profit Will Fall on Inflation Costs

-- B y   P e t e r   W o o d i f i e l d
-- 
2011-10-03T06:42:55Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-03/charles-stanley-first-half-profit-will-fall-on-inflation-costs.html
Charles Stanley Group Plc (CAY)  said first-
half profit for the period ended Sept. 30 will be lower than a
year ago because of the effect of inflation on fixed costs as
revenue in its securities unit fell on market volatility and
decline.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Peter Woodifield at 
 pwoodifield@bloomberg.net  